<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.9.2">
<l>maṉṟilma lintu kūttuvan tāṭi mālviṭai yēḻumaṭart  tāyar</l>
<l>aṉṟuna ṭuṅka vāṉirai kātta vāṇmaiko lōvaṟi yēṉnāṉ</l>
<l>niṉṟapi rāṉē nīḷkaṭal vaṇṇā nīyivaḷ taṉṉainiṉ kōyil</l>
<l>muṉṟile ḻunta muruṅkaiyil tēṉā muṉkaiva ḷaikavarn tāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Was it [your] manliness which protected the cowherd</l>
<l rend="indent">as the herders trembled,</l>
<l>Having performed briskly in the bull pen, happily dancing,</l>
<l rend="indent">and conquering seven black bulls?</l>
<l>I don’t understand! Eternal lord, you the hue of the vast sea,</l>
<l rend="indent">you snatched bangles from the forearm of this girl,</l>
<l>As [if] honey in a muruṅkai [tree] which grows in the front yard</l>
<l rend="indent">of your [own] house.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
